songs.title: 젊은 날의 Sky (Romanized)
songs.lyrics:
Olaen bam-i jinago
Dasi naeil-i chaj-aomyeon

Naui kkum-eun gakkawojilkka
Nae sigyecheoleom nan meomchwoiss-eulkka

Light in the sky
Nae jeolm-eun nal-ui sky
Neul balae wassdeon naui kkumdeuldo
Eonjengan fly fly fly

Piji moshan kkochdeuldo
Eonjenganeun pieooleugo

Guleum sog-e gadhin byeoldeuldo
Geodhin haneul-en hwanhi bichnal tende

Light in the sky
Nae jeolm-eun nal-ui sky
Neul balae wassdeon naui kkumdeuldo
Eonjengan fly fly fly

Naui bam-eun oelowo
Tto naeil-eun deo dulyeowo
Ajig-eun him-i deuljiman
Igyeonaelge

Light in the sky
Nae jeolm-eun nal-ui sky
Gin sigan sog-e meomchwo iss-eodo
Eonjengan fly fly fly

What makes you
Beautiful
Beautiful
Beautiful life

Ajig salm-eun aleumdabjanh-a
Makes you
Beautiful
Beautiful
Beautiful life
Nae kkum sog-e dah-eul ttaekkaji
Eonjenga
